        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/b3f665/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-06-13T15:46:46.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=3669104&amp;iNote=9210951\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2014 Jacques Lassaigne Champagne Autour de Minuit Les Paluets</strong></a> <em>- France, Champagne (13/06/2021)</em><br>\nRemarkable champagne, aged for three years in barrels previously used for Ganevat Vin Jaune. Native yeast, from Montgueux near Troyes. Deliciously fresh up front, orchard fruits that moves into a tangy VJ influenced midpalate, with fresh walnut, has some flesh but finishes with a really saline finish. Quite unusual and distinctive but delicious too.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/0/3/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed\" title=\"3DF3A1C0-6EF1-4E36-B2AF-8B49414E9D28.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/0/3/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed_2_666x500.jpeg\" alt=\"3DF3A1C0-6EF1-4E36-B2AF-8B49414E9D28.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"rNg9qtGMHQyjnH54UA0SE0ICdf\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/0/3/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed_2_666x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/0/3/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed_2_999x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/0/3/0324537506fb0bd824c2ad48e9008ed4f49f74ed_2_1332x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"807D70\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3DF3A1C0-6EF1-4E36-B2AF-8B49414E9D28.jpeg</span><span class=\"informations\">4032\u00d73024 2.45 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>