        "created_at": "2021-06-13T18:44:05.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"171355\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I did not even know this existed! I\u2019m leaving for France in a few days so on the hunt I\u2019ll go. It does not seem easy to find.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Tiny production!</p>\n<p>Probably only worth tracking down if you are a fan of biologically aged wines, as the influence of the Vin Jaune barrels is strong, but I absolutely love it.</p>",
